title: Jaime Harrison
added: On January 14, 2021, U.S. President-elect [[Joe Biden]] announced that Harrison would be his nominee to Chair the [[Democratic National Committee]]. As the presumptive Chair, Harrison will take office from [[Tom Perez]] after the formal election to the post scheduled to end on January 21.<ref>https://www.politico.com/news/2021/01/14/harrison-selected-as-bidens-dnc-chair-459330</ref>
